
This file documents all supported events along with their corresponding grups.


Group		Name										Values			Description

UI			SelectRequest						RequestID		Triggered to select a request in the Request Viewer
State		SelectedRequestChanged	RequestID		Triggered when the selected request has changed

Capabilities	LoadDefinition		CapabilitiesURL		Loads a capabilities definition from the given URL
Capabilities	ReloadDefinition	CapabilitiesURL		Re-loads the currently loaded capabilities definition for the PrimaryContentWindow
Capabilities	DefinitionChanged	CapabilitiesURL		Triggered when a capabilities definition has changed

UI						FirefoxMenuCommand	Name					Triggered when a Firefox menu item is clicked

Internal			OpenAllowedCapabilityHostsWindow	URL					Opens the FirePHP capabilities hosts permission window
